rows.label: tlk70000043_04_msg0001
rows.name:
Gah! How can we get Kozel-san's
spirits back to normal?

rows.label: tlk70000043_04_msg0002
rows.name:
Her eyes always look like a dead
fish's! It's a chef's job to cook
the fish, not be the fish!

rows.label: tlk70000043_04_msg0003
rows.name: Gah... I cannae leave her like this.

rows.label: tlk70000043_04_msg0004
rows.name:
If I keep visiting her, she'll
come round sooner or later...

rows.label: tlk70000043_04_msg0005
rows.name:
I can't go back to Superbia till
she's better! I'll show you the true
appetite for knowledge a chef has!
